Path: This week in Nu #12
Content:
andrasio added new 
``histogram``
 and 
``split-by``
 commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/954] #954
)
jonathandturner renamed 
``read``
 to 
``parse``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/944] #944
)
jonathandturner also added a new 
``format``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/945] #945
)
drmason13 added the ability to configure the separator used in 
``from-csv``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/943] #943
)
coolshaurya, sebastian-xyz, rtlechow, helped with writing more documentation (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/964] #964
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/965] #965
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/961] #961
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/950] #950
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/949] #949
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/948] #948
)
uma1317 fixed a bug with moving files (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/960] #960
)
sebastian-xyz also added more installation instructions to the Nu book (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/41] #41
)
